tom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Administrative konsekvenser for borgerne</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ingen</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ingen</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:2px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Klima- og miljømæssige konsekvenser</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ingen</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ingen</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:2px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Forholdet til EU-retten</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Lovforslaget indeholder ingen EU-retlige aspekter</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"height:2px;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Er i strid med de fem principper for implementering af erhvervsrettet EU-regulering / Går videre end minimumskrav i EU-regulering (sæt X)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Ja</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 1pt solid #000000;border-right: 1pt solid #000000;border-top: 1pt solid #000000;border-bottom: 1pt solid #000000;padding-left:0.2cm;padding-top:0.1cm;padding-right:0.2cm;padding-bottom:0.05cm;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">Nej</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        <div class=\"TabelTekst\">X</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"KapitelOverskrift2\">Bemærkninger til lovforslagets enkelte bestemmelser</p>\r\n<p class=\"Overskriftstekst3\">\r\n   <span class=\"Italic\">Til § 1</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Det følger af ministervederlagsloven, at ministres grundvederlag i perioden 1. april 2012-31. december 2020 er midlertidigt nedsat med 5 pct. og dermed udgør 1.185.966 kr. i årligt grundbeløb (31. marts 2017-niveau). Der henvises i øvrigt til afsnit 2.1. i lovforslagets almindelige bemærkninger.</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Det foreslås, at den midlertidige nedsættelse af grundvederlaget til ministre med 5 pct., der udløber den 31. december 2020, forlænges, således at grundvederlaget udgør 1.185.966 kr. i årligt grundbeløb (31. marts 2017-niveau) til og med 31. december 2021.</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Perioden for den midlertidige nedsættelse af ministres grundvederlag med 5 pct. foreslås forlænget til og med den 31. december 2021.</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Som konsekvens af lovforslaget, vil nedsættelsen af vederlaget til Folketingets formand ligeledes forlænges til og med den 31. december 2021.</p>\r\n<p class=\"Overskriftstekst3\">\r\n   <span class=\"Italic\">Til § 2</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Det foreslås<span class=\"Italic\">,</span> at loven træder i kraft den 1. januar 2021.</p>\r\n<p class=\"NormalInd\">Loven gælder hverken for Færøerne eller Grønland, fordi den lov, der foreslås ændret, ikke gælder for Færøerne eller Grønland og ikke indeholder en hjemmel til at sætte loven i kraft for Færøerne eller Grønland.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p><hr class=\"BilagStreg\" />\r\n<p class=\"Bilag\">Bilag 1</p>\r\n<p class=\"BilagTekst\">Lovforslaget sammenholdt med gældende lov</p>\r\n<p>\r\n   <div style=\"width:100%\">\r\n      <table class=\"Containertable\" style=\"border-style: none; border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px; \">\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"border-style: none; padding: 0px; vertical-align: top;\">\r\n               <table valign=\"top\" class=\"Maintable\" width=\"681\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse;\">\r\n                  <colgroup>\r\n                     <col width=\"244px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"23px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                     <col width=\"244px\">\r\n                     </col>\r\n                  </colgroup>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"ParallelTekstHeader\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Gældende formulering</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"ParallelTekstHeader\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Lovforslaget</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;text-align: center\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"ParallelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">§ 1</span>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">I lov om vederlag og pension m.v. for ministre, jf. lovbekendtgørelse nr. 939 af 16. juni 2017, som ændret ved lov nr. 1579 af 27. december 2019, foretages følgende ændring:</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">§ 1.</span> <span class=\"Bold\">---</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Stk. 2.</span> I perioden 1. april 2012-31. december 2020 udgør grundvederlaget 1.185.966 kr. i årligt grundbeløb (31. marts 2017-niveau).</div>\r\n                        <div class=\"NormalInd\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Italic\">Stk. 3-11.</span> ---</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\"> </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-left: 0pt none #000000;border-right: 0pt none #000000;border-top: 0pt none #000000;border-bottom: 0pt none #000000;\" valign=\"top\">\r\n                        <div class=\"ParallelTekst\">\r\n                           <span class=\"Bold\">1.</span> I <span class=\"Italic\">§ 1, stk. 2, </span>ændres »2020« til: »2021«.</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </table>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>",
